          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><span class=\"paragraph\">model = VQModel(\n    sample_size=config.image_size,\n    in_channels=1,\n    out_channels=1,</span>\n<div class=\"language-carbon highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nx\">down_block_types</span><span class=\"p\">=(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;DownEncoderBlock2D&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">&quot;DownEncoderBlock2D&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">&quot;DownEncoderBlock2D&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n<span class=\"nx\">up_block_types</span><span class=\"p\">=(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;UpDecoderBlock2D&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">&quot;UpDecoderBlock2D&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">&quot;UpDecoderBlock2D&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n\n<span class=\"nx\">block_out_channels</span><span class=\"p\">=(</span><span class=\"mi\">64</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">128</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">256</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n<span class=\"nx\">layers_per_block</span><span class=\"p\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"nx\">mid_block_add_attention</span><span class=\"p\">=</span><span class=\"nx\">False</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n\n<span class=\"nx\">latent_channels</span><span class=\"p\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"err\">#</span><span class=\"nx\">SD</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nx\">uses</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">???</span>\n<span class=\"nx\">num_vq_embeddings</span><span class=\"p\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">1024</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">#</span><span class=\"nx\">SD</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nx\">uses</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">8</span><span class=\"nx\">K</span>\n<span class=\"nx\">scaling_factor</span><span class=\"p\">=</span><span class=\"m m-Double\">0.1825</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"nx\">act_fn</span><span class=\"p\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;silu&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n\n<span class=\"nx\">norm_type</span><span class=\"p\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;group&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"nx\">norm_num_groups</span><span class=\"p\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">32</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n\n<span class=\"nx\">force_upcast</span><span class=\"p\">=</span><span class=\"nx\">False</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"err\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nx\">Keep</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nx\">FP16</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nx\">A6000</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nx\">efficiency</span>\n<span class=\"nx\">lookup_from_codebook</span><span class=\"p\">=</span><span class=\"nx\">True</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"err\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nx\">Enable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nx\">codebook</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nx\">lookup</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nx\">during</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nx\">forward</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nx\">pass</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">).to(\"cuda\")</span></span>"
